@startuml

title "Sequence Diagram: As a Customer, I want to purchase movies"

actor Customer
participant "API Client" as API
participant RoleGuard as RG
participant OrderController as OC
participant OrderService as OS
participant OrderRepository as OR
participant MovieRepository as MR

activate Customer
Customer -> API: Submit purchase request
activate API
API -> OC: POST /api/orders {movieIds, quantities, receiptName, JWT}
activate OC
OC -> RG: Validate role = CUSTOMER
activate RG
RG --> OC: Authorization result
deactivate RG

OC -> OS: Process order creation
activate OS
OS -> OS: Validate payload and business limits
OS -> OS: Validate order size <= 10 movies
OS -> OS: Validate receiptName
OS -> MR: Check movie existence and stock
activate MR
MR --> OS: Return validation data
deactivate MR
OS -> OS: Validate sufficient stock for requested movies

OS -> OR: Create order (transaction)
activate OR
OR --> OS: Return created order data
deactivate OR

OS -> MR: Update movie stock (transaction)
activate MR
MR --> OS: Confirm stock updates
deactivate MR

OS --> OC: Return operation result
deactivate OS
OC --> API: Return 201 Created + order summary
deactivate OC

API --> Customer: Display purchase confirmation
deactivate API
deactivate Customer

@enduml